== GNOME to Karmic (in launchpad) ==

This is a list mapping gnome modules from the damned lies website to the locations that they can be translated for karmic in launchpad. This way teams can keep those translations in sync.

=== GNOME - 2.28 ===

Those are the GNOME modules, ordered as they appear in the <nowiki>[[http://l10n.gnome.org/releases/gnome-2-28/|GNOME 2.28 (UI) module set]]</nowiki> page.
